# âš– 3. Comparison Operators (VERY IMPORTANT)

```js
==   ===
!=   !==
>    <    >=    <=
```

---

## ğŸ”¥ == vs ===

```js
5 == "5"  // true
5 === "5" // false
```

ğŸ§  Rule:
Always use `===`

---

## âš  Weird Comparisons

```js
null == undefined // true
null === undefined // false

NaN === NaN // false ğŸ˜±
```

To check NaN:

```js
