# ğŸ’¡ Real Developer Tips

âœ… Use `===`
âœ… Use `??` instead of `||` for defaults
âœ… Avoid complex ternaries
âœ… Use optional chaining in nested data
âœ… Avoid relying on implicit coercion
âœ… Prefer explicit conversion

